column2: SELECT to upload -- the results to the DAS (Data Archive Server) for FITS file retrieval. SELECT TOP #    p.objid,p.ra,p.dec,p.u,p.g,p.r,p.i,p.z,    p.run, p.rerun, p.camcol, p.field,    s.specobjid, s.specClass, s.z as redshift,    s.plate, s.mjd, s.fiberid FROM PhotoObj AS p    JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid WHERE    p.ra BETWEEN # AND # and p.dec BETWEEN # AND # and s.z <#
